description:
You can sure tell that Elliott loves life and loves to laugh. We both giggled our way through his photoshoot. A fun gregarious type of guy.
He's a small dude at about 5'6" but has a big thick dick that he can barely get his hand to wrap around.
You can tell he is Irish with a touch of Russian thrown in. We both had lots of fun filming this and he enjoyed showing off his stuff. I hope to work with him again and put him in the mix with other dudes.
title: Elliott - Solo
